Author: Nikolaus Phillips
Subject: Awesome sauce
Body: Edit:  not great on lollipop;  doesn't line up well.  Amazing port.  Well, more than a port, this is full of new features and integrated into common system tools.  Sending as picture works a lot better than text (LG nexus 5/ android 4.4.4) , as the text ASCII art ends up aligned badly.  But I guess it'd be aligned differently on the recipient device anyway so there's no way to make that perfect.  Anyway awesome app.  Loved the original on Linux, love this.  Thanks!
